> From: "Rob Berryhill" <racefan@...>
>
> Twinking is when a high level character gives items or help to a low level
> character. To be "twinked" would mean they were items not normally
> obtainable by a character of that level.
>
> Astur, Cleric of Brell
> Solusek Ro
